# 🌡️ Temperature Converter

## 📌 Project Overview
This is a simple and interactive Temperature Converter web application developed using **HTML5, CSS3, and Vanilla JavaScript**. It allows users to convert temperatures between **Celsius (°C), Fahrenheit (°F), and Kelvin (K)** with input validation and user-friendly error handling.

## 🚀 Features
- Enter a numeric temperature value.
- Select the input unit (Celsius, Fahrenheit, or Kelvin).
- Convert temperature with a single click.
- Displays converted values in all three units.
- Validates numeric input.
- Prevents values below absolute zero.
- Clean and responsive user interface.

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)

